===I've been planning to...===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Jade:''' I've been planning to craft a new piece of jewelry. Wanna hear the story behind it?
:{Choice} Wait, you added me as a friend?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Wait, you added me as a friend?
::'''Jade:''' In case you forgot, our paths crossed quite a bit on the Radiant Feldspar
:{Choice} Sure, but you gotta reward me for it!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Sure, but you gotta reward me for it!
::'''Jade:''' Absolutely! I promise it'll be worth your time
:{Choice} I don't know a thing about jewelry
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I don't know a thing about jewelry...
::'''Jade:''' No worries, just think of it as a casual chat
:'''Jade:''' I came into possession of a round blue natural crystal full of cleansing energy. Any guesses where it's from?
:{Choice} A jewelry store
::'''(Trailblazer):''' A jewelry store? But what made you pick that one?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I have a feeling it's not that simple
::'''Jade:''' Yes, if you only consider its appearance, it's certainly not top-grade
::'''Jade:''' If this blue crystal had been on a regular store shelf, I wouldn't have given it a second glance, much less bought it
:{Choice} A wealthy merchant's treasure vault
::'''(Trailblazer):''' A wealthy merchant's treasure vault? It must be collateral in the Bonajade Exchange
::'''(Trailblazer):''' But I get the feeling there's more to it than that
::'''Jade:''' Hmm, the Bonajade Exchange does have a plethora of treasures
::'''Jade:''' If you only consider its appearance, it's certainly not top-grade
:{Choice} Found it by the roadside
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Did you stumble upon it by the roadside?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I considered places like jewelry stores or a wealthy merchant's treasure vault, but they all seem too straightforward an answer
::'''Jade:''' Creative, but no
:'''Jade:''' Someday, maybe you'll come to realize that human greed is like a bottomless vortex
:'''Jade:''' Even if they claim a heart free of desires, they might still lose it all in a foolish moment of greed
:'''Jade:''' Just like this blue crystal &mdash; it's the condensed form of a pure planet, born from the desires of one in power
:{Choice} This is a planet?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' You turned a planet into an accessory? That's kind of terrifying!
::'''Jade:''' It takes two to make a deal. There's no coercion involved
:{Choice} Then, the Express, too...
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Are you planning to turn the Express into a crystal ornament too?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I need to tell the conductor this right away!
::'''Jade:''' Don't worry. A deal requires agreement from both parties &mdash; I'd never force anyone into making one
:'''Jade:''' I hope the story didn't scare you too much
:'''Jade:''' It seems like you don't have such desires right now. That's a good thing
:'''Jade:''' If you ever find yourself in need of making a "deal," you're always welcome at the Bonajade Exchange
}}
