===(Trailblazer), got a minute?===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Jade:''' (Trailblazer), got a minute?
:'''Jade:''' I'd like to hear your thoughts on "kids"
:{Choice} I don't have kids
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I don't have kids, so I might not be the best person to ask
::'''Jade:''' That's okay. We were all once kids anyway, so I'm really interested in hearing your views
:{Choice} Kids? That's me
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Kid at your service. Ask away!
::'''Jade:''' That's the spirit! I can't wait to hear your opinion
:'''Jade:''' What do you think will make a child happy?
:{Choice} Food, clothes, and happy family!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Being well-fed, well-clothed, and well-loved by their family &mdash; just like how the Crew is!
::'''Jade:''' Sounds like the Crew shares a really close bond. May that happiness stay with you forever
:{Choice} Free from troubles and woes!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Free from troubles and woes!
::'''Jade:''' You're right. A child's world should be innocent and carefree
:{Choice} I don't know
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I don't know
::'''Jade:''' Yeah, sometimes happiness is just hard to put into words
:'''Jade:''' I asked Topaz and Aventurine the same question
:'''Jade:''' Their definitions of happiness have changed and now vary from each other's, but on the topic of "what makes a child happy," they share the same view as you
:'''Jade:''' The children in the orphanage would probably wish for the same things too
:{Choice} The children's wishes?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' The children's wishes? Anything I can help with?
::'''Jade:''' Thanks for the offer, but I can handle it
:{Choice} You visit orphanages?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' You visit orphanages?
::'''Jade:''' Yes, I go there all the time
::'''Jade:''' You seem surprised
::{Choice} I've heard stories about the Exchange
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Well... I've heard stories about the Bonajade Exchange
::'''Jade:''' I see... No need to worry. After all, in the case of adults, choices made must be much stricter
:'''Jade:''' The kids have given me unconditional trust, and I'll reciprocate in kind with all my heart
:'''Jade:''' In any case, it's about time I head off
}}
